    However, it does not completely fix the detection of the i386 C++ path.
    See the next item.
    (Closes: #729933)
  * Bring back the path to libstdc++ under i386. Still not fixed upstream
    (Closes: #730857)
  * Define also MAXPATHLEN in Path.inc for HURD.
